  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students can compare numbers in any way that makes sense to them. Students may:</p>
<ul>
      <li>create groups of objects or draw groups of images and match to compare.</li>
      <li>use the count sequence to compare.</li>
      <li>begin to automatically know which numbers are less or more than a given number.</li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>
  
