<!-- ============================================ 
  Síntesis de la lección (discusión de cierre)
=================================================  -->
<subsubsection xml:id="lec-compararNum-sintesis" component="profesor">
  <shorttitle><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></shorttitle>
  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(5 mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><q>Diego no sabe si 7 es más que o menos que 4. ¿Cómo pueden ayudar a Diego a entender que 7 es más que 4?</q> (I could tell him to show 4 fingers on his hands and show 7 fingers on my hands so he could see 7 is more. I could tell him that when you count, you get to 4 but then you need to say more numbers to get to 7 so it is more. I know that 4 is less than 5 and 7 is more than 5.)</p>

</subsubsection>


